# 8. 獅子舞ロボと遊ぼう！

Lion Dance Robot: GROOOAR! CHOMP CHOMP CHOMP!
Tsukasa: Aaargh!!! It won't stop chasing me!!!
Lion Dance Robot: RAAARGH! CHOMP CHOMP CHOMP!
Tsukasa: Somebody help me! My legs are about to give out!
Len: Hang in there, Tsukasa! Help's on the way!
KAITO: Miku, Len, are you ready?
Miku: Yup! All good here!
KAITO: Then let's begin Operation Lion Capture!
Miku & Len: Yeah!
Emu: Whaaam!
Miku: Got it!
Emu: Slaaam!
Miku: My goodness, Emu! You were born to make mochi!
Emu: Yay! I got praised by Miku! Let's make the most delicious mochi ever☆
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP!
Emu: Oh, Lion Dance Robot! Wanna help us make mochi?
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP CHOMP!
Emu: Alright! Let's make them together!
Rui: I'm glad you've become such good friends with the Lion Dance Robot. It was worth staying up all night working on it.
Len: It's so lifelike. It's unbelievable! But why did you decide to make it...?
Rui: Hehe. I wanted to make a robot to go along with the time of year.
Rui: I cloned Robo-Nene's operating system, but its AI is original and lets it move autonomously.
Len: Wow! Um, that sounds so high tech! But it's a really cool robot, nonetheless!
Nene: Sorry, but can someone help us out? I need someone to help cut mochi cakes.
MEIKO: I'm happy to help! Let's do it together♪
Tsukasa: It's great to see everyone so happy and full of energy on New Year's Day!
KAITO: Yes. It's a nice time to just relax. Lately, I've been stuck thinking up ideas for a new show...
Tsukasa: Oh, you're working on a new show?
KAITO: Yes. Miku found this gigantic net and wanted to use it for a performance, but I'm having trouble finding a way to include it...
KAITO: Speaking of which, where did you get the mochi mortar and mallet from? Looks like they've already been used quite a bit...
Tsukasa: Oh, that was all Emu. She found them in a storehouse at her house.
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP CHOMP!
Tsukasa: Whoa, what do you want? Weren't you making mochi with Emu?
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP!
Rui: I think it likes you, Tsukasa. Maybe try playing with it.
Tsukasa: With me? Well, okay... I can play with it for a bit if...
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP
Tsukasa: Oww! Cut it out! Hey, don't chew on my head! Stop it or I won't play with you!!
Miku: Okay, great! We're almost done here!
Emu: Yeah! Okay, one last push! Whaaam!
Miku: Ready!
Emu: Whaaam!
Miku: Ready!
Emu: Slaaaaam!!!
Emu: Hm...?
Miku: Uh oh, the mallet flew out of Emu's hands!
KAITO: Tsukasa! Watch out!!
Tsukasa: What the...?! Why's there a mallet flying towards me...?!
Tsukasa: Hey, Lion Dance Robot! We have to move or...!
Lion Dance Robot: CHOMP?!
Emu: Nooo!!! I'm so sorry, Lion Dance Robot! I let the mallet fly out of my hands and...
Miku: Hm? Lion Dance Robot? It's gone all quiet...
Lion Dance Robot: ...
Tsukasa: Hey, say something!
Lion Dance Robot: ...
Tsukasa: Is it broken...? Rui, can you take a look and...?
Lion Dance Robot: GR, GRR, GRRRRR...
Tsukasa: Huh?
Lion Dance Robot: CHOOOMP!!!
Tsukasa: What the...?!
Lion Dance Robot: RAAARGH! CHOMP CHOMP CHOMP!!!!
Tsukasa: S-Stop! Stay away from me!!
Tsukasa: Wh-What's going on...?!
